## Background

The Gail Score is a risk assessment tool to quantify a woman's risk for developing invasive breast cancer. Certain factors, such as age, race, and ancestral history can be indicative of future development. Based on a woman's Facebook profile, this model aims to quantify the risk of invasive breast cancer. For further information, see <http://www.cancer.gov/bcrisktool>.
